<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
  		<meta charset="utf-8">
  		<title>Redirectron: <%= script %> in Pythonista</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<p>This page will redirect you to Pythonista to run your <%= script %> script. Remember to add it to you Home Screen so you can do this quicker in the future.</p>
		<script type="text/javascript">
		var count = 1;
		var redirect = "pythonista://" + <%= script %> + "?action=run";
		 
		function countDown(){
		    var timer = document.getElementById("timer");
		    if(count > 0){
		        count--;
		        timer.innerHTML = "This page will redirect in "+count+" seconds.";
		        setTimeout("countDown()", 1000);
		    }else{
		        window.location.href = redirect;
		    }
		}
		</script>
		 
		Hope this is helpful!
		<br>
		 
		<span id="timer">
		<script type="text/javascript">countDown();</script>
		</span>
	</body>
</html>